{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a7f2c5e0-1b4d-4e9c-9a2f-bitmonie000001",
    "name": "Bitmonie API — v1.1",
    "description": "All endpoints grouped by module, plus simulated provider webhooks. v1.1 adds accrual-based pricing, partial repayments, add-collateral, and a permanent per-user PalmPay VA.\n\n**End-to-end happy-path flow:**\n1. Open → Variables tab → set `blink_webhook_secret`, `blink_account_id`, `blink_wallet_btc_id` to match `.env`. Defaults wired to the local `.env`.\n2. `Auth → Signup` (defaults to `bitmonie-smoke@example.com` / `TestPass123!` — change to your own).\n3. Grab OTP from Mailgun inbox for `user_email`, paste into `Auth → Verify Email` and run.\n4. `Auth → Login` — session token auto-populates `session_token` and rides as a cookie on subsequent requests.\n5. `KYC → tier-1` — on success, the user's permanent NGN repayment VA is provisioned (read it out of the DB into `virtual_account_no` for the PalmPay webhook later).\n6. `Disbursement Accounts → add BANK` — name-matched against your User row first (KYC fallback).\n7. `Loans → calculate` — see projections (origination + projected interest + projected custody for chosen term).\n8. `Loans → checkout` — creates loan, returns Blink invoice; capture `loan_id` + `payment_hash`.\n9. `Webhooks → blink (collateral confirmed)` — flips loan PENDING_COLLATERAL → ACTIVE, dispatches NGN disbursement.\n10. (After some days) `Webhooks → palmpay (collection — repayment received)` — auto-credits via the waterfall. Use the same VA number from step 5.\n\n**v1.1 add-on flows:**\n- `Loans → add-collateral` — fresh variable-amount Lightning invoice; mirror with the Blink webhook (use the new `topup_payment_hash`) to bump `collateral_amount_sat` while staying ACTIVE.\n- `Loans → claim-inflow` — when a customer has 2+ ACTIVE loans (auto-match impossible) or after an unmatched-inflow ops alert.\n\n**Collection pre-request hook** auto-injects `Idempotency-Key: <uuid>` on every POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE (skipped on webhook routes).\n\n**Webhook folder** pre-request scripts compute valid Svix (Blink) signatures from `blink_webhook_secret` before sending.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "const mutating = ['POST', 'PUT', 'PATCH', 'DELETE'];",
          "if (mutating.includes(pm.request.method) && !pm.request.headers.has('Idempotency-Key')) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'Idempotency-Key', value: pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}') });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
