            "description": "Current buy/sell rates for SAT_NGN, BTC_NGN, USDT_NGN. Cached 90s in Redis. Returns 422 if stale >2 minutes."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /v1/loans/calculate",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/loans/calculate?principal_ngn=300000&duration_days=7",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "loans", "calculate"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "principal_ngn", "value": "300000" },
                { "key": "duration_days", "value": "7" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Public loan quote calculator (v1.1 — accrual-based pricing).\n\nReturns:\n- **Locked at origination:** `origination_fee_ngn` (`ceil(principal/100k) × 500`), `daily_custody_fee_ngn` (`ceil(initial_collateral_usd/100) × 100`), `daily_interest_rate_bps = 30` (0.3%).\n- **Projections** (estimates for the chosen duration — actual fees accrue daily): `projected_interest_ngn`, `projected_custody_ngn`, `projected_total_ngn`.\n- **Collateral sizing:** `collateral_amount_sat`, `initial_collateral_usd` (sourced from Blink BTC/USD), `sat_ngn_rate_at_creation`.\n- **UI thresholds** (these move daily once accrual starts): `initial_liquidation_rate_ngn`, `initial_alert_rate_ngn`.\n\nMin loan ₦50,000 / max ₦10,000,000 self-serve. Min 1 day / max 90 days."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
